AI Therapist ‚Äì Mental Health 

Neo is an AI-powered mental health assistant designed to offer empathetic, context-aware conversations in a natural, Gen-Z‚Äìfriendly tone. It integrates sentiment analysis to adapt responses based on the user‚Äôs emotional state, making interactions feel more supportive and personalized.

The project was built to explore how conversational AI can lower barriers to mental health support by providing an always-available, judgment-free space for reflection. Neo is not a replacement for professional care, but a complementary tool that helps users articulate thoughts, track mood patterns, and engage in meaningful self-dialogue.

---

## ‚ú® Features

* ü§ñ AI-powered empathetic conversations (Grok LLM)
* üß† Context-aware chat sessions
* ‚ö° Real-time messaging using WebSockets
* üîä Speech-to-text and text-to-speech support
* üóÉÔ∏è Session storage using SQLite
* üñ•Ô∏è React-based frontend
* üîê API key‚Äìbased authentication (no hardcoded secrets)

---

## üõ† Tech Stack

### Backend

* **Python 3.10 / 3.11**
* Flask
* Flask-SocketIO
* SQLite
* Grok API (LLM inference)
* faster-whisper (speech-to-text)
* edge-tts / pyttsx3 (text-to-speech)

### Frontend

* React (Create React App)
* Node.js 18 LTS
* npm

---

## üìÅ Project Structure

```
AI_Therapist/
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ backend/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ app.py
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ services/
