## ‚ö†Ô∏è Prerequisites

### Software Required

| Software | Version      |
| -------- | ------------ |
| Python   | 3.10 or 3.11 |
| Node.js  | 18 LTS       |
| Git      | Latest       |

---

## üöÄ Setup Instructions (Corrected)

### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Clone the Repository

```cmd
git clone https://github.com/ayushhirlekar/AI_Therapist.git
cd AI_Therapist
```

---

## üîß Backend Setup

### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Create & Activate Virtual Environment

```cmd
cd backend
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
```

---

### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Install Backend Dependencies

```cmd
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

### 4Ô∏è‚É£ Configure Environment Variables (IMPORTANT)

Create a `.env` file inside `backend/`:

```env
GROK_API_KEY=your_grok_api_key_here
```

‚ö†Ô∏è **Never commit `.env` to GitHub**

---

### 5Ô∏è‚É£ Start Backend Server

```cmd
python app.py
```

Expected:

```
Running on http://localhost:8000
```

Test:

```
http://localhost:8000/health
```

---

## üé® Frontend Setup

### 6Ô∏è‚É£ Install Frontend Dependencies

Open a **new terminal**:

```cmd
cd AI_Therapist\frontend
npm install
```

---

### 7Ô∏è‚É£ Start Frontend

```cmd
npm start
```

Open:

```
http://localhost:3000
```

---

## ‚ñ∂Ô∏è Running the Application

### Backend (Terminal 1)

```cmd
cd backend
venv\Scripts\activate
python app.py
```

### Frontend (Terminal 2)

```cmd
cd frontend
npm start
```

